metadata.name: An angel and a demon
metadata.description:
I am a demon from the depths of hell,
But you have captured me in your spell,
You are an angel that fell from the sky,
I have caught you and help you to fly.

You are an angel with all your beauty,
For I will protect you because it's my duty,
I am a demon with my dark charm,
You have helped me and held my arm.

I am a demon with wings like a bat,
And have dark eyes almost like a cat,
You are an angel with beautiful white wings,
Shining so bright like a diamond in rings.

We glide thru the sky and thru the clouds,
Past the sun and all the crowds,
Our love is said to be forbidden,
But we shall not be hidden.

An angel and a demon that we are,
But our love for each other will take us far,
There is one more thing before I go,
For I know our hearts will forever glow.
